[ProMED-mail does not normally post reports on HIV/AIDS, but the magnitude
of the problem in South Africa and the continuing reticence of the South
African Government require that the South African Medical Research Council
Report be given wider exposure. The MRC report is based on figures obtained
in the period 1999-2001, and there has been no subsequent MRC report. - Mod.CP]
